{"tid":1710582,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[緊急] 簡單暴大支援地點說明 For 想入去支援既人","createTime":"2019-11-12T08:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T11:37:51.000Z","uid":125760,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"dfa006f0232718c19757b3253d86ba4dc3751375","tid":1710582,"uid":125760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"兩號橋位置如下，如果要幫手請順便路行上去，唔會有校巴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mO4nNaK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmO4nNaK.png&h=23e8cb20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\npdf檔<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://epymt.math.cuhk.edu.hk/pdf/LSK_map.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepymt.math.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fpdf%2FLSK_map.pdf&d=UyoO8KdNfTPb55o7yEEco258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=3e33fd80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epymt.math.cuhk.edu.hk/pdf/LSK_map.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前線需要火水，玻璃樽及平常你諗到既抗爭物品，有就盡量帶啲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">最後最重要要帶既就係你個人！！</span><br />\n<br />\n黎唔到既爭快18區開花，分散警力保護暴大"},{"pid":"b15e7034199e85c1d32e355b9f6562fc702184bf","tid":1710582,"uid":125760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:07:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eadd2907433cdc9ba0ea4c1ea29a5df4f6f69549","tid":1710582,"uid":125760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:07:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51ada75a275772c270388b1815fab3fa31ba3ff8","tid":1710582,"uid":125760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:07:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06a847e83f8b837e103f5635239ae2e212650624","tid":1710582,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87bdff8bc6148d4c853a3d96fef7ba59f2a2c078","tid":1710582,"uid":